{"tid":983371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咪扮睇唔明】英大學涉歧視中国學生 警告勿cheating加註現代漢語「舞弊」","createTime":"2019-01-16T02:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T04:30:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"98d6b6f348933092e40dc4aee85adf7c2183e81f","tid":983371,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547603281_af4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547603281_af4d.jpg&h=d25b7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文電郵附加一個敏感詞的中文字解釋，算不算歧視？英國利物浦大學（University of Liverpool）近日向外國留學生發送了一封電郵，提醒他們在考試期間作弊的嚴重後果，卻因在英文字cheating後特別用中文「舞弊」作註解，令來自中國的學生十分不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有中國留學生向校方表達不滿，認為有關做法具爭議。校方隨後回覆指，這是因為「學校的中國學生通常不熟悉cheating這一英文單詞，所以我們提供了它的中文繙譯『舞弊』」。<br />\n<br />\n這個解釋令在該校就讀的中國留學生更加不滿，他們認為校方不該在發給所有國際學生的英文郵件中，單獨使用中文解釋敏感詞彙，此舉明顯涉嫌歧視，會讓人覺得來自中國的學生都有作弊的可能。<br />\n<br />\n校方後來又發聲明，就事件所引發的誤解致歉之餘，還表示之前發出有關考試的提醒，並非針對某任特定學生群體。不過，校方仍堅持，因為以往出現過中國學生對英文術語不理解，加上中文繙譯只是為了更好地傳達考試規範。<br />\n<br />\n內地網友對今次事件反應兩極，有網友認為，「應該自省自律，反思中國留學生到底是否存在作弊較為嚴重的情況。感覺涉嫌歧視，還是談不上。」但亦有人指，「哪個留學生會連『Cheating』是甚麼意思都不知道？未免太針對中國人了」、「我看是中國學生成績太好你們懷疑是『舞弊』來的，分明是嫉妒！」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190116/59148299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59148299&d=e6KkJSHDiHBqtimTWL5KH3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5ed5012c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59148299&h=387ac3b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190116/59148299</a>"},{"pid":"103d48ee603e4b9098b07a8f973b36f5b30ff2e2","tid":983371,"uid":15830,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:07:39.000Z","msg":"哪個留學生會連『Cheating』是甚麼意思都不知道？<br />\n<br />\n出貓比人周到嘅咪唔識咩叫Chearing<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8dcd96544d4230a23b7c860d8b25dd7330e032","tid":983371,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:13:52.000Z","msg":"又針對中國人 唔識cheating 有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n你重要譯做舞弊<br />\n<br />\n咁又唔係選舉<br />\n<br />\n你係咪侮辱我哋中國人嘅智慧<br />\n<br />\n英文國家大撚晒呀"},{"pid":"30eac5f89221123fddc7aebce1ae7158e7791421","tid":983371,"uid":152476,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:23:48.000Z","msg":"係囉唔好去英國讀書，返強大祖國啦"},{"pid":"a9f73b82bdefa5ddcf7a9d96e3a6d3e9112ff839","tid":983371,"uid":68556,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:25:00.000Z","msg":"識你又扮唔明<br />\nPeople's Republic of Cheating"},{"pid":"c961e657583b81e62043cde0f424deb93063a091","tid":983371,"uid":35430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:26:51.000Z","msg":"正正常常個班香港學生同台仔真係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係血源詛咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生個亞洲人樣但唔係支那人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1485895a1d7511450588ff20340fb0e34a74db3","tid":983371,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"香港新加坡台灣馬拉加拿大華人留學生都唔care,係得中國果班覺得俾人歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9596e87d8558655258a3c0dc5067638ff6223fc","tid":983371,"uid":188176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"學校的中國學生通常不熟悉cheating這一英文單詞，所以我們提供了它的中文繙譯『舞弊』<br />\n<br />\